snippet.title: U.S Yoshi's Story commercial
snippet.description: This is the U.S commercial version for the Yoshi's Story game for N64. This commercial show adolecents with largue tongues broking objects and more.. And show a animated Yoshi's Story box. Good commercial! Um bom comercial do Yoshi's Story para os E.U.A.
